==English==

===Noun===
'''epexegesis'''

# Additional explanation or explanatory material.
#:''I'm afraid we've run up against the bamboo curtain—that is to say, an economic and political barrier in the East as real as the iron curtain has been in the West''

==Etymology==

Greek epexegesis, from epexegeisthai, to explain in detail: ep-, epi-, epi- + exgeisthai, to explain

